releaseNotes:
1. Added the NullBuilder class (implements an IBundleBuilder interface) that responsible for prevention of early combining of code;
2. Implemented analogs of the StyleBundle and ScriptBundle classes for the Bundle Transformer: CustomStyleBundle (uses CssTransformer as transformation by default and NullBuilder as builder by default) and CustomScriptBundle (uses JsTransformer as transformation by default and NullBuilder as builder by default);
3. In the css configuration element added the disableNativeCssRelativePathTransformation attribute, which disables native transformation of relative paths to absolute in CSS-files.
